The best parts to keep are:
- The `#1 public good / #2 speculative research / #3 SaaS bootstrap` split. That is the cleanest explanation of the governance attack surface.
- The more honest use of Chaos Labs as both validation and warning.
- The suggestion to reframe sustainability as maintenance funding for public infrastructure, not “here is our paid tier.”
