- Sustainability: add a post-grant maintenance section with exit clause
- Evidence Appendix E3: remove “would have flagged”; use “is designed to detect” / “signal was readable on-chain”
- Technical Appendix: no substantive change

## Sustainability framing
- The grant funds public infrastructure
- The professional tier exists only as the maintenance path for that infrastructure
- Add exit clause: if the professional tier does not reach $150K ARR within 18 months of Phase 1 delivery, Sigma Labs transitions operational tooling and maintenance procedures to a community-run model and publishes a full handover package

